            "last_activity_date": 1583936396,
            "creation_date": 1583936396,
            "body": "<p>If you have text which has <strong>|||<\/strong> in it you can split it in a string array by the following regular expression <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>String text = \"abc|||123|||#@&amp;\"\nString[] splitarray = text.split(\"\\\\|\\\\|\\\\|); // using double slash so | is not interpreted as OR \nfor(String s : splitarray)\n  {\n   System.out.println(s);\n   }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>output :<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>     abc\n     123\n     #@&amp;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
